description: Jed Athens"The Ass-Wrecker"Ht: 6'3"Wt: 205lbsSeason W/L Record (0-0)Jessie Colter"Cut-Throat"Ht: 6'2"Wt: 200lbsSeason W/L Record (3-3) Newcomer Jed "Ass-Wrecker" Athens comes to Naked Kombat with collegiate wrestling under his belt, and not to mention military background. title: Jed "Ass-Wrecker" Athens vs Jessie "Cut-Throat" Colter
